title: Sarh — Property approval (3/3) · Delivery + public verify (PDF + on-chain)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Citizen
    actor V as Public verifier
    participant W as apps/web (Angular)
    participant API as .NET 8 API
    participant DB as SQL Server
    participant FS as Storage<br/>(local FS)
    participant BC as Blockchain<br/>(Ethereum / Hyperledger)

    Note over C,V: 6) Delivery + public verify (PDF + on-chain)
    C->>W: open /app/my/properties → download PDF + view NFT
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/storage/deeds/<id>.pdf
    API->>FS: read file
    FS-->>C: PDF (with QR pointing to /verify/<code>)

    V->>W: scan QR / open /verify/<code>
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/verify/:code
    API->>DB: SELECT property + verify hash + nft
    API->>BC: ownerOf(tokenId)
    BC-->>API: current owner address
    API-->>V: 200 { owner, area, decree, signed: true,<br/>nft: { tokenId, contract, network, txHash, currentOwner } }